<plot>"Unconditional" tells the compelling story of how a seven-year old boy's unconditional love for his mother prevails over the destructiveness of her drug addiction. Set in a run-down California neighborhood, a young boy struggles to find his place amid the chaos of his mother's loveless one-night stands and all-night drug binges. Despite her downward spiral, this courageous little boy's love for his mother never falters, and we see how it deepens when she is nearly taken from him.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?629052</url></doc>
